0,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T09:41:59.000Z","msg":"我個振，將所有衫褲棉，放入密氣袋，放臭丸，加DE粉，焗2,3禮拜<br />\n幾乎所有嘢都要放喺密氣袋，全部都要加DE粉<br />\n佢有時候會躲埋啲書到<br />\n-<br />\n然後，拆床，全部拎入廁所，沖100度熱水<br />\n封晒張床嘅所有窿窿罅罅，用膠紙又好，五金舖買啲膠擠落去，總之封晒啲窿窿<br />\n然後用DE粉，散落成間房，包括張床，書架，電腦枱，角落位置<br />\n-<br />\n你可以去第二間房到瞓，但要確保自己啲衫唔好有蟲<br />\n你自己間房，要丟空兩個禮拜<br />\n兩個禮拜之後<br />\n全滅"},{"pid":"b8cbb5fc44b45af8068ee6b97984389e196197db","tid":2010580,"uid":32667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d989613656640d3d1929abbe92c73e3a2df62e2","tid":2010580,"uid":34935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T09:23:45.000Z","msg":"聽滅蟲公司講 千祈唔好自己炸"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T09:42:56.000Z","msg":"唔識野，炸左，邊之成屋係，攪左半年先攪掂"},{"pid":"ee6e48d3f383aead12efed410e7106d858c5f2e5","tid":2010580,"uid":32667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b459fa1a2a2ed64bf8c8c5c33c34aef22d904024","tid":2010580,"uid":246690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5004250972541f7c5fac1150a6d74a788deda19f","tid":2010580,"uid":32667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T07:37:54.000Z","msg":"之前都有，攪到成屋係，搵滅蟲攪左半年消失晒🤘🏼"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T09:22:03.000Z","msg":"邊間滅蟲？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T09:43:19.000Z","msg":"留tg"},{"pid":"bc57edd06f2c5c6328374326e960ea2ad955fcc1","tid":2010580,"uid":231054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T09:44:35.000Z","msg":"兩年前中過，真係惡夢黎，果時要全屋傢俬換過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71c0168129e405cc034a0f4e8d54e46ac9e39f63","tid":2010580,"uid":290640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"292bf610a0b7048ca0d0a589e13930100ef80709","tid":2010580,"uid":246690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d267574661c0469208d71a531ff3e444fd89b63b","tid":2010580,"uid":290640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f8437f81c8952d2db2214e64e80703a3a940ad6e","tid":2010580,"uid":246690,"like":0,"dislike"